y^2 &amp;amp;= r^2 - (x_{i+1})^2 \\
d_1 &amp;amp;= y_i^2 + (x_{i+1})^2 - r^2 \\
d_2 &amp;amp;= r^2 - ((x_{i+1})^2 + (y_i - 1)^2)
\end{align*}
