x&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= x_r + (x - x_r) \cos \theta - (y - y_r) \sin \theta \\
y&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= y_r + (x - x_r) \sin \theta + (y - y_r) \cos \theta
\end{align*}
